com.morpheus.sdk.infrastructure

Class ListServersRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.morpheus.sdk.internal.AbstractApiRequest<ListServersResponse>
      • com.morpheus.sdk.infrastructure.ListServersRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApiRequest<ListServersResponse>

    public class ListServersRequest
extends AbstractApiRequest<ListServersResponse>
    A request object for defining a request for fetching a list of servers within the Morpheus Account. Typically this object is called from the MorpheusClient instance and is used to fetch a list of Server objects along with the total count in the ListServersResponse. Example Usage: 
         
     	MorpheusClient client = new MorpheusClient(credentialsProvider);
     	ListServersRequest request = new ListServersRequest().max(50).offset(0);
     	ListServersResponse response = client.listServers(request);
